Privacy Policy

Instrumentation Calculator

Effective Date: September 10, 2025.

We value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how the Instrumentation Calculator app handles your information.

Information Collection

No Personal Data Collected:
This app does not collect, store, or share any personal information such as name, email, phone number, or location.

No Background Tracking:
The app works entirely offline. Your calculations remain on your device and are never transmitted to any server.

Data Usage

All calculations (flow, pressure, temperature, etc.) are performed locally on your device.

No user data is accessed, logged, or stored by the developer.

Third-Party Services

The app does not use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

